#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>You didn't import demo data?</strong> You can still do it. Go to "
"Apps &gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade your Hardware Shop package and check the "
"related box."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Har du ikke importeret demodata endnu?</strong> Du kan stadig nå "
"det. Gå til Apps &gt; Brancher &gt; Opdatér din pakke til hardwarebutikker, "
"og markér det relevante felt."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><span style=\"color: "
"#875A7B;\">Website</span></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders "
"directly in Odoo and go live with your <strong><span style=\"color: "
"#875A7B;\">E-shop</span></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"En gratis, personlig og integreret <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\""
">hjemmeside</span></strong> med få klik. Begynd at modtage ordrer direkte i "
"Odoo, og gå live med din <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\""
">e-shop</span></strong> på få minutter."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Ace Hardware is already registered in your database; select it using the "
"\"Customer\" button."
msgstr ""
"Ace Hardware er allerede registreret i din database. Vælg det ved at klikke "
"på knappen \"Kunde\"."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add your customer, and the product they want."
msgstr "Tilføj dine kunder og det produkt, som de gerne vil have."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any specific manufacture process in your shop? (Cutting wood panels, "
"assemblies...). Try the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Manufacture "
"App</span></strong>"
msgstr ""
"Er der særlige fremstillingsprocesser i din butik (f.eks. skæring af "
"træpaneler, samlinger osv.)? Prøv <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">"
"Produktionsappen</span></strong>"

