#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Hello there!\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            You just installed the Odoo for Hardware Shop package. By doing so, we have installed a bunch of necessary apps to run your shop efficiently.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo offers to improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"Hej!\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Du har netop installeret Odoos pakke til byggemarkeder, som "
"automatisk har installeret en række nødvendige apps, så din butik kan drives "
"effektivt.\n"
"            <br/><br/>\n"
"            Få indsigt i de grundlæggende funktioner i denne pakke, og "
"udforsk de mange muligheder, Odoo tilbyder, for at optimere din oplevelse."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:hardware_shop.product_attribute_value_7
msgid "High"
msgstr "Høj"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you go back to your Point of Sale, you can start a new order for 5 units "
"of Asian. Water Proofing Hydroloc for Ferrous Hardware, another B2B "
"customer."
msgstr ""
"Når du vender tilbage til kassesystemet, kan du oprette en ny ordre på 5 "
"enheder af \"Asian: Vandtæt fugemasse\" til Ferrous Hardware, en anden B2B-"
"kunde."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you navigate to your \"Purchase App\", you can see that a new Purchase "
"Order for Ferrous Hardware has been automatically generated. It will ensure "
"a replenishment for Asian. Water Proofing Hydroloc."
msgstr ""
"Når du går til din \"Indkøbsapp\", kan du se, at der automatisk er oprettet "
"en ny ordre til Ferrous Hardware. Dette sikrer, at en ny sending af \"Asian: "
"Vandtæt fugemasse\" bliver leveret."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import demo data and try the Use Case."
msgstr ""
"Hvis du vil følge den praktiske vejledning i dette modul, bør du importere "
"demodataene og afprøve brugsscenariet."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.template,name:hardware_shop.product_template_104
msgid "JK Wall Putty Fine"
msgstr "JK Wall Putty Fine"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Let's say your customer Ace Hardware just called you to order 30 Asian. "
"Water Proofing Hydroloc."
msgstr ""
"Lad os sige, at din kunde Ace Hardware netop har ringet for at bestille 30 "
"stk. \"Asian: Vandtæt fugemasse\"."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo <strong><span "
"style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Marketing Automation</span></strong>, "
"<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Email Marketing</span></strong>, "
"<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Social Media "
"Marketing</span></strong>, and <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">SMS "
"Marketing</span></strong>"
msgstr ""
"Administrér alle dine kommunikationskanaler ét sted med Odoo <strong><span "
"style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Automatiseret marketing</span></strong>, <strong>"
"<span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">E-mailmarketing</span></strong>, <strong>"
"<span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Markedsføring på sociale medier</span></"
"strong> og <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">SMS-marketing</span></"
"strong>"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Accounting "
"App</span></strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Administrér din bogføring nemmere end nogensinde i et fuldt integreret miljø."
"(<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Bogføringsappen</span></strong>)"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.template,name:hardware_shop.product_template_70
msgid "Mario Super Water Tank"
msgstr "Mario Super-vandtank"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Navigate to the Inventory App and select \"X to process\" in the Delivery "
"Orders."
msgstr "Gå til Lager-appen, og vælg \"X skal behandles\" under leveringsordrer."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Navigate to your Sales App. You can now create a new Sales Order by clicking"
" the \"New\" button, top left."
msgstr ""
"Gå til Salgsappen. Du kan nu oprette en ny salgsordre ved at klilkke på "
"knappen \"Ny\" øverst til venstre."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Notice that if you need the delivery to be paid by your customer, you can "
"create a delivery product and add it to its cart. In this demo, you can use "
"the \"POS Delivery\" to add a 5,00 Excl. Taxes delivery price."
msgstr ""
"Bemærk, at du kan oprette et leveringsprodukt og tilføje det til "
"indkøbskurven, hvis leveringen skal betales af kunden. I denne demo kan du "
"bruge \"POS-levering\" til at tilføje en leveringspris på 5,00 kr. ekskl. "
"moms."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that we have placed all these orders, it's time to purchase missing "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Nu, hvor alle ordrer er afgivet, er det tid til at købe de manglende "
"produkter."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone into"
" an additional scanner (and much more)."
msgstr ""
"Odoo er fuldt integreret i én app. Download den, og forvandl din telefon til "
"en ekstra scanner (og meget mere)."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo giver dig ubegrænsede muligheder, såsom:"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Oversigten viser naturligvis kun de funktioner, der følger med pakken. Du "
"kan tilføje nye apps, redigere eller slette demodata og prøve dig frem!"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the order is placed, you can see that the top left button switches to "
"\"Receive products\". Click it to open your receipt order and validate it to"
" confirm that this product is back in stock."
msgstr ""
"Når ordren er afgivet, vil du se, at knappen øverst til venstre skifter til "
"\"Modtag produkter\". Klik på den for at åbne ordrebekræftelsen og bekræfte, "
"at produktet igen er på lager."

